                    <span>This book gives an excellent chronologic sequence of beginning and eventual rise of Intel. It is pager turner from the 1st page. Also, gives a very clear visibility to an outsider of how well and menacingly Intel built its empire and business. A great book for anyone interested in knowing the history of Intel and semiconductor sector.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Fair and Balance reporting.  Great Motivational stories!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
